::Shredder::

Shredder growls silently as Mantella mentions Quickstrike. He hated the small 
fuzor as well, for a few different reasons.

"Same here," he says, "I nearly killed him a few times. Probably should have 
finished him off when I had the chance."

He looks back at Mantella again. "I hate him for power reasons. Why do you 
hate him?"
